ens%20of%20students%20complained%20of%C2%A0vomiting%2C%20diarrhea%2C%20and%20stomach%20cramps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20local%20Evanston%20eatery%20advertised%20%241%20burritos%20for%20students%2C%20deal-seeking%20undergrads%20rushed%20in%20to%20fill%20their%20bellies%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0only%20to%20soon%20empty%20them%20again.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20%241%20burrito%20promotion%20offered%20by%20local%20%26quot%3Bno-frills%26quot%3B%20Mexican%20restaurant%20Big%20Wig%20Tacos%20%26amp%3B%20Burritos%20on%20November%2018%20has%20reportedly%20triggered%20a%20minor%20outbreak%20of%20norovirus%20among%20Northwestern%20University's%20student%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%20with%20the%20Evanston%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20Department%2C%20shortly%20after%20consuming%20food%20from%20the%20restaurant%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20promotion%2C%20students%20began%20complaining%20of%20norovirus%20symptoms%20such%20as%20vomiting%2C%20diarrhea%2C%20and%20stomach%20cramps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Big%20Wig%20Tacos%20%26amp%3B%20Burritos'%20cooperation%2C%20investigators%20are%20working%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20specific%20origin%20of%20the%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highly%20infectious%20norovirus%20spreads%20quickly%20in%20settings%20like%20college%20campuses%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20cruise%20ships%20if%20proper%20hand%20hygiene%20protocols%20are%20not%20thoroughly%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20say%20the%20restaurant%20will%20undertake%20a%20deep%20cleaning%20during%20a%20planned%20temporary%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20patrons%20who%20ate%20at%20Big%20Wig%20Tacos%20%26amp%3B%20Burritos%20on%20the%20date%20of%20the%20promotion%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20fill%20out%20a%20related%20health%20questionnaire%20to%20aid%20containment%20efforts%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are%20not%20exhibiting%20symptoms.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBig%20Wig%20Tacos%20%26amp%3B%20Burritos%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburrito-promotion-norovirus-outbreak-northwestern-university-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700789497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655ffce04ca513d8242e1e34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburrito-promotion-norovirus-outbreak-northwestern-university-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20%241%20burrito%20promotion%20led%20to%20a%20%232%20issue%20among%20the%20student%20body%20of%20Northwestern.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jswearingen%40insider.com%20(Jake%20Swearingen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburrito-promotion-norovirus-outbreak-northwestern-university-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Income%20Tax%20Data%20Reveals%20That%20Increase%20in%20Compliance%20Is%20Marginal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F01171239%2Findian-rupee-money-cash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Board%20of%20Direct%20Taxes%20(CBDT)%20has%20released%20data%20on%20income%20tax%20payees%20for%20financial%20years%202013-14%20to%202022-23.%20More%20detailed%20data%20about%20different%20categories%20of%20tax%20payees%20are%20available%20for%20the%20financial%20year%202020-21.%20This%20data%20can%20be%20used%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20income%20distribution%20of%20the%20top%20income%20earners%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFew%20direct%20tax%20payers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20tax%20is%20paid%20by%20a%20minuscule%20percent%20of%20the%20population.%20Official%20data%20shows%20that%207.4%20crore%20individuals%20filed%20tax%20returns%20in%20FY2022-23%20and%206.75%20crore%20in%20FY2020-21.%20In%20this%20earlier%20year%2C%20there%20were%20also%202.1%20crore%20people%20who%20did%20not%20file%20a%20tax%20return%20but%20paid%20Tax%20Deducted%20at%20Source%20(TDS).%20So%2C%20in%20FY2020-21%2C%20effectively%20there%20were%208.85%20crore%20people%20in%20the%20tax%20net%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%206.6%25%20of%20the%20population.%20Since%20we%20do%20not%20have%20corresponding%20data%20on%20those%20not%20filing%20tax%20return%20but%20paying%20TDS%20for%20FY%202022-23%2C%20we%20do%20not%20yet%20know%20the%20total%20number%20of%20entities%20in%20the%20tax%20net%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20paying%20income%20tax%20or%20filing%20a%20tax%20return%20has%20to%20have%20an%20income%20above%20the%20income%20tax%20exemption%20limit%20and%20therefore%20has%20to%20be%20among%20the%20top%20income%20earners%20in%20the%20country.%20What%20is%20their%20distribution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exemption%20limit%20for%20determining%20tax%20liability%20is%20now%20Rs%203%20lakh%20but%20has%20been%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%2C%20with%20some%20concessions%20for%20senior%20and%20super%20senior%20citizens.%20With%20a%20standard%20deduction%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20rebate%20under%20Section%2087A%2C%20till%20now%20an%20individual%20did%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20any%20tax%20up%20to%20a%20taxable%20income%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh.%20Of%20India%E2%80%99s%20per%20capita%20annual%20income%20at%20current%20prices%20of%20Rs%201%2C50%2C007%20in%202021-22%2C%20this%20is%20333%25.%20From%20the%20current%20financial%20year%2C%20tax%20will%20have%20to%20be%20paid%20at%20income%20of%20above%20Rs%207.5%25%2C%20414%25%20of%20the%20likely%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20about%20Rs%201%2C81%2C000.%20So%20those%20in%20the%20tax%20net%20are%20in%20the%20tail%20of%20the%20income%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20much%20concession%2C%20for%20FY2020-21%2C%20out%20of%206.76%20crore%20e-returns%20filed%2C%204.46%20crore%20paid%20nil%20tax%20(67.3%25%20of%20the%20total).%20The%202.1%20crore%20who%20did%20not%20file%20a%20return%20but%20paid%20TDS%20must%20have%20had%20an%20income%20below%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%2C%20otherwise%20they%20would%20have%20had%20to%20file%20a%20return.%20Adding%20these%20two%20numbers%2C%20effectively%2C%206.6%20crore%20returns%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%208.85%20crore%20(73.4%25)%20were%20filed%20by%20those%20with%20low%20incomes.%2091%20lakh%20(10.3%25%20of%20those%20in%20the%20tax%20net)%20had%20taxable%20incomes%20above%20Rs%209.5%20lakh%20and%20who%20can%20be%20called%20well-off%20in%20the%20Indian%20context.%20About%202.15%20lakh%20declared%20income%20above%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20maybe%20characterised%20as%20wealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20brief%2C%20people%20in%20top%20rung%20of%20the%20income%20ladder%20in%20the%20country%20were%20those%20who%20were%20in%20the%20income%20tax%20net%20(6.6%25%20of%20the%20population)%20even%20if%20they%20did%20not%20pay%20income%20tax.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%20only%200.68%25%20of%20the%20population%20were%20the%20really%20well%20off%20who%20effectively%20paid%20income%20tax.%20Further%2C%200.016%25%20declared%20an%20income%20above%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20had%20a%20share%20of%2038.6%25%20of%20the%20taxable%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaveats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20picture%20of%20the%20well-off%2C%20characterised%20by%20those%20who%20effectively%20pay%20income%20tax%2C%20is%20incomplete.%20Two%20additional%20factors%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%20First%2C%20the%20rich%20families%20split%20up%20their%20incomes.%20This%20enables%20them%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20concessions%20on%20each%20of%20the%20returns%20filed%20and%20each%20of%20the%20incomes%20may%20then%20fall%20in%20the%20lower%20income%20bracket%20on%20which%20a%20lower%20tax%20rate%20may%20apply.%20Second%2C%20the%20well-off%20resort%20to%20black%20income%20generation%20by%20not%20declaring%20their%20true%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20point%20implies%20that%20the%200.68%25%20people%20who%20paid%20significant%20amounts%20of%20income%20tax%20belong%20to%20an%20even%20smaller%20percent%20of%20the%20families.%20So%2C%20the%20actual%20family%20income%20of%20the%20well-off%20is%20much%20higher.%20Since%20the%20poor%20face%20unemployment%2C%20under%20employment%20and%20joblessness%2C%20their%20family%20income%20is%20not%20much%20higher%20than%20what%20a%20poor%20individual%20earns.%20The%20implication%20is%20that%20the%20gap%20in%20family%20incomes%20between%20the%20well-off%20and%20the%20poor%20would%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20much%20larger%20than%20gap%20in%20incomes%20shown%20by%20the%20data%20on%20individuals%20paying%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20black%20incomes%20are%20generated%20by%20the%20well-off%2C%20who%20have%20substantial%20incomes.%20Those%20who%20have%20an%20income%20below%20the%20taxable%20limit%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20hide%20their%20income.%20They%20do%20not%20have%20to%20file%20a%20return%20or%20declare%20their%20income%20to%20the%20tax%20authorities.%20Those%20who%20have%20a%20taxable%20income%20of%2C%20say%2C%20up%20to%20Rs%209.5%20lakh%2C%20need%20pay%20only%20a%20few%20percent%20of%20it%20as%20tax%2C%20if%20they%20take%20advantage%20of%20deductions%20under%2080C%2C%2080D%2C%2080TTA%2C%20etc.%20So%20they%20will%20hardly%20benefit%20from%20hiding%20their%20income%20and%20will%20not%20be%20generators%20of%20black%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20well-off%2C%20especially%20businessmen%20and%20professionals%20who%20declare%20a%20lower%20income%20to%20tax%20authorities%20so%20as%20to%20pay%20a%20smaller%20portion%20of%20their%20income%20as%20tax.%20Some%20of%20them%20completely%20escape%20the%20tax%20net%20by%20not%20filing%20a%20return%20or%20by%20showing%20an%20income%20below%20the%20taxable%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20factors%20lead%20to%20the%20official%20data%20underestimating%20the%20skewedness%20of%20income%20distribution%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHas%20compliance%20increased%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organised%20sector%20has%20higher%20incomes%20and%20contributes%20most%20to%20direct%20taxes.%20It%20produces%2055%25%20of%20the%20GDP.%20Its%20share%20of%20GDP%20would%20have%20risen%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20disproportionately%20hit%20the%20unorganised%20sector.%20The%20GDP%20was%20Rs%201%2C98%2C00%2C914%20crore%20in%20FY%202020-21%2C%20the%20Covid%20year.%20So%2C%20Rs%201%2C08%2C90%2C000%20crore%20should%20have%20been%20captured%20in%20the%20tax%20net%20from%20the%20organised%20sector.%20Some%20more%20should%20have%20come%20from%20the%20few%20well-off%20businesses%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailed%20data%20for%20FY%202020-21%20shows%20that%20the%20taxable%20income%20declared%20by%20all%20return%20filers%20was%20Rs%2069%2C59%2C552.48%20crore.%20This%20is%20about%2035.15%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20and%20about%2063.9%25%20of%20what%20should%20have%20been%20shown%20as%20declared%20incomes%20by%20the%20organised%20sector.%20On%20this%20declared%20income%2C%20the%20tax%20collected%20was%20Rs%209%2C47%2C176%20crore.%20The%20tax%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20was%20a%20very%20low%204.78%25.%20If%20black%20income%20generation%20were%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20it%20would%20be%20even%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20FY2021-22%2C%20GDP%20recovered%20from%20its%20low%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20became%20Rs%202%2C36%2C64%2C637%20crore.%20The%20direct%20tax%20collection%20increased%20to%20Rs%2014%2C12%2C422%20crore%2C%20so%20that%20the%20direct%20tax%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20rose%20to%205.97%25.%20In%202018-19%2C%20this%20figure%20was%20even%20higher%20at%206.02%25.%20But%2C%20even%20this%20figure%20is%20low%20compared%20to%20many%20developing%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20claims%20that%20more%20and%20more%20people%20are%20filing%20tax%20returns%20and%20presents%20this%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20better%20tax%20compliance%20and%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20black%20economy.%20According%20to%20the%20data%20just%20released%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20paying%20direct%20taxes%20has%20risen%20from%207%2C42%2C49%2C558%20in%20FY2016-17%20to%209%2C37%2C76%2C869%20in%20FY2021-22.%20This%20is%20impressive%2C%20but%20the%20catch%20is%20that%20most%20of%20the%20people%20entering%20the%20tax%20net%20declare%20nil%20income%20or%20a%20low%20income%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reduction%20in%20black%20income%20generation%20would%20have%20meant%20that%20many%20more%20of%20the%20individuals%20with%20high%20incomes%20would%20have%20come%20into%20the%20tax%20net%2C%20and%20the%20direct%20tax%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20should%20have%20risen%20sharply%20instead%20of%20hovering%20between%205.5%25%20and%206%25%20since%202014-15.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20tax%20returns%20is%20due%20to%20the%20constancy%20of%20the%20income%20at%20which%20a%20tax%20return%20needs%20to%20be%20filed%20remaining%20unchanged%20at%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%2C%20while%20incomes%20have%20risen%20due%20to%20inflation.%20The%20per%20capita%20net%20national%20income%2C%20which%20tells%20us%20how%20much%20an%20average%20citizen%20is%20earning%2C%20is%2030.1%25%20higher%20in%202022-23%20than%20it%20was%20in%202019-20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20someone%20with%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20in%20FY2019-20%2C%20pre%20pandemic%2C%20would%20be%20earning%20Rs%202.6%20lakh%20in%20FY2022-23.%20In%202019-20%2C%20she%20would%20not%20have%20had%20to%20file%20a%20tax%20return%20while%20in%202022-23%20she%20would%20have%20to%20file%20a%20return.%20Thus%2C%20the%20number%20of%20tax%20return%20filers%20would%20automatically%20rise.%20But%20the%20tax%20they%20pay%20would%20not%20rise%2C%20so%20their%20entry%20into%20the%20tax%20net%20does%20not%20impact%20the%20tax%20to%20GDP%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20income%20tax%20data%20released%20recently%20points%20to%20the%20highly%20skewed%20nature%20of%20income%20distribution%20in%20the%20country%20with%20only%20about%200.68%25%20people%20paying%20effective%20taxes.%20The%20percentage%20of%20families%20they%20belong%20to%20would%20be%20even%20smaller.%20If%20tax%20manipulations%20by%20the%20wealthy%20and%20black%20income%20generation%20are%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20then%20the%20income%20distribution%20becomes%20even%20more%20skewed.%20Finally%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20tax%20filers%20is%20due%20to%20inflation%20but%20this%20has%20hardly%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20direct%20tax%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20since%20most%20new%20entrants%20in%20the%20tax%20net%20file%20either%20nil%20return%20or%20are%20exempt%20from%20tax.%20So%2C%20tax%20compliance%20in%20the%20country%20has%20hardly%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArun%20Kumar%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EUnderstanding%20Black%20Economy%20and%20Black%20Money%20in%20India%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700789416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F01171239%2Findian-rupee-money-cash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fincome-tax-data-reveals-that-increase-in-compliance-is-marginal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20income%20tax%20data%20released%20recently%20points%20to%20the%20highly%20skewed%20nature%20of%20income%20distribution%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20only%20about%200.68%25%20people%20paying%20effective%20taxes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fincome-tax-data-reveals-that-increase-in-compliance-is-marginal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anti-immigration%20rioters%20in%20Dublin%20torched%20vehicles%20and%20looted%20stores%20after%20a%20knife%20attacker%20injured%203%20children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20talks%20with%20an%20