attice%20girder%20rib%2C%20impeded%20the%20further%20insertion%20of%20the%20rescue%20pipe.%20At%202%3A30%20am%2C%20gas%20cutters%20were%20deployed%20to%20remove%20the%20metallic%20obstacle%2C%20allowing%20the%20pipe%20to%20be%20extended.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20has%20implemented%20a%20five-pronged%20action%20plan%20to%20rescue%20the%20trapped%20workers%2C%20with%20five%20agencies%3A%20Oil%20and%20Natural%20Gas%20Corporation%2C%20Sutluj%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%2C%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%2C%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20and%20Tehri%20Hydro%20Development%20Corporation%20-%20each%20assigned%20specific%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESituated%20about%2030%20km%20from%20Uttarkashi%20and%20a%20seven-hour%20drive%20from%20Dehradun%2C%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20central%20government's%20Char%20Dham%20all-weather%20road%20project.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700789340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fe3ppdcn_uttarakhand-tunnel-pti-_625x300_24_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-uttarakhand-tunnel-op-enters-final-stretch-to-rescue-trapped-workers-4601405%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rescue%20efforts%20for%20the%2041%20workers%20trapped%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20entered%20Day%2013%20today.%20Drilling%20operations%20had%20to%20be%20halted%20temporarily%20yesterday%20as%20cracks%20were%20identified%20in%20the%20platform%20supporting%20the%20drilling%20machine%2C%20an%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-uttarakhand-tunnel-op-enters-final-stretch-to-rescue-trapped-workers-4601405%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-uttarakhand-tunnel-op-