arents%20to%20avoid%20apple%20cinnamon%20fruit%20pouches%20from%203%20specific%20brands%20while%20investigating%20their%20role%20in%20giving%20dozens%20of%20toddlers%20elevated%20blood%20lead%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20November%2022%2C%20the%20FDA%20has%20received%2052%20reports%20of%20high%20lead%20blood%20levels%20in%20children%20exposed%20to%20the%20pouches%2C%20per%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Foutbreaks-foodborne-illness%2Finvestigation-elevated-lead-levels-cinnamon-applesauce-pouches-november-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagency%20update.%3C%2Fa%3E%20All%20reported%20cases%20have%20been%20found%20in%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20continues%20its%20investigation%2C%20the%20agency%20specifically%20recommended%20avoiding%20the%20WanaBana%2C%20Weis%2C%20and%20Schnucks%20brands%2C%20which%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20recalled%20from%20all%20Dollar%20Tree%20retailers%2C%20per%20the%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20yet%20clear%20exactly%20where%20the%20contamination%20point%20for%20the%20pouches%20was%2C%20though%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwellness%2F2023%2F11%2F07%2Fapplesauce-recalls-lead-exposure-testing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20cinnamon%20as%20a%20possible%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELead%20poisoning%20of%20any%20volume%20can%20be%20extremely%20dangerous%20for%20anyone%2C%20but%20even%20more%20so%20for%20young%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnceh%2Flead%2Fprevention%2Fhealth-effects.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenters%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20child%20is%20exposed%20to%20lead%20by%20touching%2C%20swallowing%2C%20or%20breathing%20it%20in%2C%20it%20can%20have%20severe%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20low%20levels%20of%20lead%20in%20blood%20have%20been%20shown%20to%20negatively%20affect%20a%20child's%20intelligence%2C%20ability%20to%20pay%20attention%2C%20and%20academic%20achievement%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20agency's%20site.%20%26quot%3BThe%20effects%20of%20lead%20poisoning%20may%20be%20permanent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20isn't%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20lead%20exposure%2C%20the%20CDC%20considers%20anything%20over%20a%20blood%20lead%20level%20of%203.5%20micrograms%20per%20deciliter%20to%20be%20higher%20than%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChildren%20reported%20to%20the%20FDA%20were%20found%20to%20have%20blood%20lead%20levels%20from%204%20to%2029%20micrograms%20per%20deciliter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FHealth%2FwireStory%2Fchildren-sickened-fruit-pouches-tainted-lead-fda-105110506%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20ABC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20is%20recommending%20any%20child%20who%20may%20have%20consumed%20the%20impacted%20products%20be%20screened%20for%20lead%20poisoning%2C%20which%20can%20be%20done%20through%20a%20blood%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-sick-lead-tainted-applesauce-pouches-fda-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700780493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655fccbd4ca513d8242e1b19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-sick-lead-tainted-applesauce-pouches-fda-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20of%20November%2022%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20received%2052%20reports%20of%20high%20lead%20blood%20levels%20in%20exposed%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22scahill%40businessinsider.com%20(Sebastian%20Cahill)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-sick-lead-tainted-applesauce-pouches-fda-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20Is%20%26quot%3BFighter%26quot%3B%2C%20Will%20Give...%3A%20Supriya%20Sule%20On%20Poll%20Body%20Notice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20said%20that%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfighter%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20give%20a%20%26quot%3Bdignified%20and%20honest%26quot%3B%20reply%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20notice%20over%20his%20%26quot%3BJaibkatra%26quot%3B%20(pickpocket)%20and%20%26quot%3BPannauti%26quot%3B%20remarks%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20an%20election%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20is%20a%20strong%20and%20honest%20leader.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20he%20will%20give%20a%20dignified%20and%20honest%20answer.%20He%20is%20a%20fighter.%20He%20can%20afford%20to%20be%20fearless%20because%20he%20is%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sule%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20so%20many%20examples%20of%20BJP%20talking%20about%20his%20family.%20So%2C%20now%20if%20he%20speaks%20something%2C%20why%20is%20there%20a%20need%20to%20feel%20bad%3F%20They%20(BJP)%20had%20even%20talked%20about%20his%20great%20grandfather.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20on%20Thursday%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20the%20Congress%20MP%20on%20the%20BJP's%20complaint%20to%20the%20ECI%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20allegedly%20made%20derogatory%20remarks%20in%20his%20poll%20rallies%20against%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhereas%2C%20a%20complaint%20has%20been%20received%20from%20the%20BJP%20(copy%20enclosed)%20alleging%20that%20you%2C%20on%20November%2022%2C%202023%2C%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20Bayatu%2C%20District%20Barmer%2C%20Rajasthan%20made%20wild%20allegations%20and%20spoke%20in%20a%20derisive%20and%20obnoxious%20manner%20about%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20comparing%20a%20PM%20to%20a%20%26quot%3BJaibkatra%26quot%3B%20(pickpocket)%20and%20using%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BPannauti%26quot%3B%20is%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20very%20senior%20leader%20of%20a%20National%20Political%20Party.%20Further%2C%20the%20allegation%20of%20grant%20of%20waivers%20of%20Rs%2014%2C00%2C000%20crores%20for%20the%20past%209%20years%2C%20is%20asserted%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20not%20borne%20out%20on%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ECI%20letter%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurthermore%2C%20they%20are%20allegedly%20in%20violation%20of%20Section%20123%20(4)%20of%20the%20R.P.%20Act%2C%20Section%20171G%2C%20504%2C%20505%20(2)%2C%20and%20499%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Barmer%20claimed%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20presence%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20was%20the%20reason%20behind%20India's%20World%20Cup%20final%20loss%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20guys%20were%20playing%20well%2C%20they%20would%20have%20won%20the%20world%20cup.%20But%20'Pannauti'%20made%20us%20lose.%20The%20TV%20guys%20won't%20tell%20you%20this%20but%20people%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20while%20campaigning%20at%20Rajasthan's%20Barmer%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20further%20asked%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20explain%20why%20the%20action%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20against%20him%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccordingly%2C%20you%20are%20requested%20to%20provide%20your%20explanation%2C%20on%20the%20allegation%20made%20and%20to%20show%20causes%20as%20to%20why%20action%20as%20deemed%20fit%20for%20alleged%20violation%20of%20MCC%20and%20relevant%20penal%20provisions%20is%20not%20initiated%20by%20the%20Commission.%20Your%20reply%2C%20if%20any%2C%20be%20reached%20by%2018.00%