%2F23230436%2FA-Baraat-procession-Wikimedia-Comm.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Bari%20and%20Bauri%20(61%2C003%20and%203%2C250%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20must%20have%20seen%20them%20in%20your%20neighbourhood.%20The%20people%20we%20are%20going%20to%20discuss%20today%20have%20a%20unique%20identity%20and%20role.%20One%2C%20they%20bear%20a%20light%20on%20their%20forehead%20as%20a%20ritual%20during%20weddings.%20Second%2C%20they%20make%20leaf%20plates%2C%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Epattal%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Edauna%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20are%20still%20used%20to%20serve%20food%20in%20weddings%20in%20rural%20areas.%20We%20are%20talking%20about%20Bari%20and%20Bauri%20castes.%20Those%20who%20remained%20Hindu%20were%20called%20Bari%2C%20while%20those%20who%20converted%20were%20called%20Bauri.%20This%20is%20also%20a%20different%20aspect%20of%20this%20country%E2%80%99s%20socio-religious%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20art%20of%20making%20leaf%20plates%20is%20a%20tribal%20profession%20which%20dates%20back%20to%20a%20time%20when%20neither%20copper%20nor%20iron%20were%20used%2C%20that%20is%2C%20before%20the%20era%20of%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation.%20There%20are%20two%20reasons%20for%20it.%20Firstly%2C%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation%20was%20an%20urban%20civilisation%20and%20tribalism%20was%20not%20present%20in%20its%20bare%20form.%20One%20might%20even%20say%20that%20by%20that%20time%20tribal%20arts%20had%20become%20refined.%20Secondly%2C%20there%20is%20evidence%20of%20the%20use%20of%20bronze%20and%20copper%20during%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation%20period.%20Such%20utensils%20have%20been%20unearthed%20during%20excavations%20at%20Mohenjodaro.%20A%20metallic%20statue%20of%20a%20dancer%20was%20also%20recovered.%20It%20was%20obviously%20not%20Bari%20and%20Bauri%20people%20who%20made%20those%20utensils%20and%20statues.%20However%2C%20the%20lifespan%20of%20leaf%20plates%20is%20very%20short%20and%20they%20turn%20to%20dust%20soon%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20337px)%2085vw%2C%20337px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22337%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22482%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20development%20of%20any%20civilisation%20should%20not%20be%20viewed%20in%20the%20ascending%20order%20because%20then%20the%20things%20that%20come%20first%20in%20the%20order%20of%20ascension%20become%20secondary.%20But%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20Bari%20and%20Bauri%20people%20must%20have%20been%20one%20of%20the%20first%20inhabitants%20of%20the%20country.%20Before%20copper%20and%20bronze%20utensils%2C%20potters%20made%20earthen%20vessels.%20But%20that%20too%20can%20be%20considered%20an%20urban%20invention.%20Before%20potters%2C%20it%20must%20have%20been%20Bari%20and%20Bauri%20people%20who%20made%20leaf%20vessels%20for%20consuming%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20sound%20completely%20futile%20now%20but%20for%20their%20ancestors%2C%20it%20must%20have%20been%20a%20novel%20idea.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20they%20should%20be%20given%20credit%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20avoid%20eating%20food%20off%20the%20ground.%20It%20was%20not%20puritanism%20but%20a%20sense%20of%20cleanliness.%20Eating%20food%20off%20the%20ground%20causes%20soil%20particles%20to%20get%20added%20to%20the%20food.%20Secondly%2C%20due%20to%20food%20particles%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20many%20diseases%20getting%20spread%20due%20to%20rotting%20leftover%20grains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20looks%20at%20it%20from%20this%20perspective%2C%20one%20will%20realise%20how%20important%20the%20invention%20of%20%3Cem%3Edauna%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Epattal%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas.%20Without%20it%2C%20even%20the%20expensive%20and%20modern%20equipment%20used%20today%20would%20not%20exist.%20But%20this%20great%20invention%20was%20not%20given%20any%20place%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bari%20and%20Bauri%20people%20still%20live%20in%20many%20states%20of%20North%20India%20such%20as%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Delhi.%20In%20Jharkhand%2C%20they%20are%20included%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20category%2C%20whereas%20in%20Bihar%2C%20they%20are%20categorised%20as%20an%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Indian%20historians%20ignored%20them%20when%20recording%20history%20but%20foreign%20historians%20have%20mentioned%20them%2C%20though%20barely%2C%20in%20their%20research%20reports.%20For%20example%2C%20Robert%20Wayne%20Russell%20in%20his%20report%20described%20these%20people%20as%20a%20caste%20of%20domestic%20servants%20and%20nurses.%20He%20also%20describes%20them%20as%20the%20makers%20of%20leaf%20plates%2C%20who%20reside%20in%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussell%20also%20wrote%20that%20the%20Bauri%2FBari%20people%20light%20torches%20and%20act%20as%20torch%20bearers%20in%20marriages%20and%20other%20events%20and%20during%20journeys.%20Some%20of%20them%20have%20taken%20up%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Caste%20Census%20Survey%20Report-2022%20released%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Bihar%2C%20they%20have%20been%20mentioned%20as%20two%20separate%20castes.%20As%20for%20those%20who%20are%20Hindus%2C%20their%20number%20is%20stated%20to%20be%2061%2C003%20while%20those%20who%20still%20remain%20with%20non-Hindu%20identity%20are%203%2C250.%20This%20number%20is%20proof%20enough%20that%20they%20still%20exist%20and%20no%20matter%20what%20religion%20they%20follow%2C%20they%20do%20not%20reject%20their%20%E2%80%98Bari%2FBauri%E2%80%99%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%2058-year-old%20Vishwanath%20Bari%20of%20Bari%20caste%20lives%20in%20Narhi%20village%20of%20Dulhin%20Bazar%20block%20of%20Patna%20in%20Bihar.%20Vishwanath%20Bari%E2%80%99s%20father%20Ramdhyan%20Bari%20died%20in%202015%20while%20climbing%20a%20tree%20to%20pluck%20leaves.%20After%20his%20death%2C%20Vishwanath%20Bari%E2%80%99s%20family%20stopped%20making%20leaf%20plates.%20However%2C%20he%20cites%20another%20reason%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20market%20is%20no%20longer%20as%20profitable%20as%20before.%20He%20said%20that%20Palash%2C%20Bad%2C%20Bahera%20and%20Mahua%20leaves%20were%20used%20to%20make%20pattal.%20It%20was%20a%20laborious%20task%20which%20involved%20plucking%20leaves%20from%20the%20trees%2C%20sorting%20them%20out%20and%20tying%20them%20together%20using%20a%20straw%2C%20drying%20them%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20leaving%20them%20overnight%20to%20soak%20moisture%20and%20then%20packing%20them%20into%20bundles%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20Bari%20said%20that%20even%20the%20trees%20have%20disappeared%20now%20and%20so%20leaves%20are%20also%20not%20available.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20work.%20Now%2C%20he%20and%20his%20three%20sons%20work%20as%20daily%20wage%20labourers.%20Except%20the%20house%20in%20which%20they%20live%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20own%20even%20a%20bit%20of%20agricultural%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20Bari%20said%20that%20he%20belongs%20to%20the%20family%20of%20Rupan%20Bari%2C%20who%20is%20mentioned%20as%20the%20commander%20of%20Alha%20Udal%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Mahoba.%20In%20the%2011th%20century%2C%20Alha%20Udal%20had%20defeated%20Prithviraj%20Chauhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussell%20was%20right.%20These%20people%20could%20not%20sustain%20themselves%20only%20by%20making%20%3Cem%3Edauna%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epattal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20so%20they%20acquired%20other%20professions.%20This%20includes%20the%20profession%20of%20torchbearer%20which%20consisted%20of%20three%20tasks.%20One%20is%20to%20put%20oil%20in%20the%20torch%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3Emashaal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20second%20is%20to%20ignite%20it%20on%20time%20and%20third%20is%20to%20carry%20it%20when%20required%2C%20for%20instance%20during%20a%20journey%2C%20as%20Russell%20has%20written.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20carrying%20a%20torch%20does%20not%20always%20illuminate%20the%20torchbearer%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20just%20as%20a%20lamp%20has%20darkness%20beneath%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20foreign%20historian%2C%20M.A.%20Sherring%2C%20described%20these%20people%20as%20an%20aboriginal%20tribe%20and%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Bari%2FBauri%20caste%20has%20only%20one%20%3Cem%3Egotra%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20unique%20occupation%20is%20making%20plates%20and%20cups%20from%20leaves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20they%20also%20work%20as%20torch%20bearers%20and%20barbers.%20Since%20they%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20time%20collecting%20leaves%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20they%20are%20not%20only%20engaged%20in%20the%20business%20of%20plucking%20leaves%20but%20also%20chopping%20trees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20do%20not%20possess%20land%20undertake%20various%20other%20jobs.%20It%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20from%20one%20type%20of%20work.%20Bari%20and%20Bauri%20also%20never%20depended%20on%20one%20job.%20Therefore%2C%20they%20remained%20associated%20with%20sanitation%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20caste%20is%20gradually%20becoming%20extinct.%20All%20those%20castes%20are%20facing%20a%20threat%20of%20extinction%20whose%20traditional%20occupations%20have%20now%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260835%2Fbihar-caste-survey-bari-bauri-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0