C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20terrorist%2C%20who%20was%20hiding%20behind%20a%20Sangar%20(stone%20structures%20in%20the%20forest)%20and%20firing%20intermittently%20was%20subsequently%20eliminated.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20one%20of%20the%20two%20terrorists%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Quari%2C%20a%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20sniper%20and%20explosives%20expert%20who%20was%20active%20in%20Rajouri%20for%20over%20a%20year.%C2%A0%20He%20was%20involved%20in%20at%20least%20three%20terror%20incidents%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuari%20was%20known%20to%20be%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20%23Dangri%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20six%20innocent%20civilians%20were%20killed%20in%20Jan%2023%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%23Kandi%20attacks%20in%20the%20%23rajouri%20%23poonch%20areas.%20He%20was%20instrumental%20in%20the%20revival%20of%20terrorism%20in%20these%20districts%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20post%20from%20the%20official%20account%20of%20the%20Army's%2016%20Corps%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700746380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ft04u1ps8_captain-mv-pranjal-captain-shubham-gupta-and-havildar-abdul-majid_625x300_23_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-how-the-encounter-in-jammu-and-kashmir-unfolded-4600149%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dense%2C%20low%20visibility%20forests%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20and%20its%20uphill%20terrain%20had%20cost%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20army%20officers%20and%20three%20soldiers%20during%20the%20two-day%20gunbattle%20with%20terrorists%20at%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri.%20Two%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20have%20been%20eliminated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-how-the-encounter-in-jammu-and-kashmir-unfolded-4600149%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-how-the-encounter-in-jammu-and-kashmir-unfolded-4600149%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-how-the-encounter-in-jammu-and-kashmir-unfolded-4600149%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Prakash%20Raj%20Summoned%20In%20Rs%20100-Crore%20Ponzi%20Scam%20Linked%20To%20Jeweller%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Prakash%20Raj%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20questioning%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20100-crore%20Ponzi%20scheme%20linked%20to%20a%20jeweller.%20Mr%20Raj%20was%20the%20brand%20ambassador%20of%20Pranav%20Jewellers%2C%20a%20chain%20accused%20of%20running%20the%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20raided%20branches%20of%20the%20Trichy-based%20jewellery%20chain%2C%20which%20has%20branches%20in%20several%20places%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%2C%20including%20Chennai%2C%20for%20allegedly%20running%20a%20Ponzi%20scheme%20and%20duping%20investors%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20who%20had%20been%20the%20brand%20ambassador%20of%20the%20jeweller%20for%20a%20significant%20period%2C%20has%20not%20given%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20matter%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stores%20run%20by%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20shut%20down%20in%20October%20and%2C%20based%20on%20complaints%2C%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Trichy%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%20owner%2C%20Madhan.%20Lookout%20notices%20had%20also%20been%20issued%20against%20the%20owner%20and%20his%20wife%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20in%20a%20statement%20yesterday%20said%20Rs%20100%20crore%20had%20been%20collected%20by%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20gold%20investment%20scheme%20that%20promised%20high%20returns.%20Not%20only%20did%20the%20returns%20not%20materialise%2C%20but%20the%20amount%20invested%20had%20also%20not%20been%20given%20back