ver-fears-that-russia-is-behind-a-migrant-influx%2Famp_articleshow%2F105450589.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-sends-border-police-reinforcements-to-finland-over-fears-that-russia-is-behind-a-migrant-influx%2Famp_articleshow%2F105450589.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Will%20Proposed%20Criminal%20Laws%20Curb%20Marriages%20Through%20Deceit%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20bills%20to%20replace%20British-era%20criminal%20laws%20were%20adopted%20recently%20by%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Home%20Affairs.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20replace%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973%3B%20along%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%20(BNS)%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%2C%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Adhiniyam%20Bill%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%2C%20were%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20on%20August%2011%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20All%2010%20opposition%20members%20in%20the%20panel%20gave%20a%20dissenting%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20new%20sections%20in%20the%20proposed%20bills%20cleared%20by%20the%20MPs'%20panel%2C%20aimed%20at%20checking%20crimes%20against%20women.%20The%20new%20bills%20include%20a%20specific%20provision%20in%20which%20marrying%20a%20woman%20after%20%26quot%3Bsuppressing%20identity%26quot%3B%20or%20indulging%20in%20sex%20under%20the%20false%20pretence%20of%20marriage%20could%20warrant%20jail%20as%20well%20as%20a%20fine.%20Section%2069%20of%20the%20BNS%20Bill%2C%202023%20seeks%20to%20prosecute%20those%20who%20marry%20a%20woman%20by%20'deceitful%20means'.%20The%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bdeceitful%20means%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20defined%20to%20include%20the%20false%20promise%20of%20employment%20or%20promotion%2C%20or%20inducement%20or%20'marrying%20after%20suppressing%20identity'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20proposed%20legislation%2C%20the%20punishment%20for%20sex%20by%20'deceitful%20means'%20or%20'false%20promises%20of%20marriage'%20is%20up%20to%2010%20years%20of%20imprisonment.%20This%20is%20being%20construed%20by%20some%20as%20directed%20towards%20interfaith%20marriages%2C%20specifically%20%26quot%3Blove%20jihad%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20term%20that%20the%20right-wing%20uses%20for%20Muslim%20men%20seducing%20Hindu%20women%20into%20converting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20feel%20the%20clause%20safeguards%20girls%20and%20women%20who%20are%20sexually%20exploited%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20marriage%20or%20forced%20to%20convert.%20With%20the%20new%20clause%2C%20it%20will%20be%20considered%20an%20offence%20if%20the%20man%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20marrying%20the%20woman%20at%20the%20time%20of%20making%20the%20promise.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20did%20not%20address%20sex%20based%20on%20false%20promise%20of%20marriage.%20Such%20cases%20were%20usually%20handled%20under%20Section%2090%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20which%20deems%20consent%20obtained%20through%20'misconception%20of%20fact'%20invalid.%20The%20law%20was%20open%20to%20interpretation%20and%20culprits%20went%20scot-free%2C%20mostly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20groups%20have%20often%20raised%20allegations%20about%20'love%20jihad'%20and%20Muslim%20men%20%26quot%3Btrapping%26quot%3B%20Hindu%20women%20into%20romantic%20relationships%20with%20the%20motive%20of%20converting%20them%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20demographic%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalita%20Malhan%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20counsellor%20who%20runs%20an%20NGO%20and%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20claimed%20several%20incidents%20of%20girls%20barely%2011%20or%2012%20years%20old%20lured%2C%20sexually%20exploited%20and%20left%20pregnant.%20The%20girls%20are%20then%20cajoled%20into%20converting%20for%20marriage.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20these%20girls%20come%20from%20poor%20families%20and%20the%20police%20never%20accept%20their%20parents'%20complaints.%20Even%20educated%20girls%20have%20been%20trapped%20under%20false%20identities%20for%20marriage%20and%20sexually%20exploited.%20This%20new%20clause%20will%20benefit%20hundreds%20of%20vulnerable%20girls%20who%20suffer%20in%20silence%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20BJP-ruled%20states%20have%20brought%20in%20laws%20against%20forced%20conversion%2C%20justifying%20them%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20allegedly%20increasing%2C%20or%20even%20rampant%2C%20instances%20of%20Muslim%20men%20deceitfully%20marrying%20Hindu%20women.%20States%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20have%20brought%20in%20laws%20to%20check%20'love%20jihad'.%20The%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20also%20investigated%20several%20cases%2C%20especially%20from%20Kerala.%20The%20Kerala%20cases%20were%20flagged%20by%20the%20Catholic%20Bishops'%20Council%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20Christian%20girls%20were%20not%20spared%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20too%20was%20considering%20enacting%20the%20law%20on%20similar%20lines.%20In%20June%202018%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20High%20Court%20granted%20divorce%20in%20an%20alleged%20'love%20jihad'%20case%20in%20which%20the%20accused%20allegedly%20lied%20about%20his%20religion%20and%20forced%20the%20victim%20to%20convert%20to%20Islam%20after%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20BJP-ruled%20states%20have%20cracked%20down%20on%20so-called%20love%20jihad%2C%20relying%20on%20a%20populist%20move%20aimed%20at%20gaining%20the%20support%20of%20the%20party's%20core%20voters.%20The%20proposed%20new%20criminal%20laws%2C%20if%20passed%20before%20the%202024%20election%2C%20is%20bound%20to%20colour%20the%20campaign.%20The%20opposition%20will%20naturally%20be%20critical%20of%20any%20such%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20legal%20experts%20insist%20there%20is%20nothing%20like%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20that%20adult%20men%20and%20women%20are%20free%20to%20marry%20and%20also%20convert%3B%20this%20is%20enshrined%20under%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20religion.%20The%20subject%20of%20relationship%20and%20marriage%20are%20personal%20and%20best%20left%20to%20those%20involved.%20Criminalising%20'a%20promise%20to%20marry'%20is%20invasion%20of%20people's%20lives%20and%20their%20fundamental%20Right%20to%20Privacy.%20Determining%20whether%20a%20promise%20to%20marry%20has%20been%20made%20can%20be%20subjective%20and%20challenging%20to%20prove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20present%20laws%20allow%20for%20the%20punishment%20for%20a%20person%20who%20conceals%20his%20identity%2C%20gets%20married%20and%20has%20sex%20with%20the%20woman.%20There%20was%20no%20need%20to%20bring%20any%20special%20thing%20on%20this%20because%20it%20is%20already%20covered%20by%20existing%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Colin%20Gonsalves%2C%20senior%20advocate%2C%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20man%20can%20falsely%20represent%20to%20a%20woman%20that%20%26quot%3Bnow%20you%20have%20sex%20with%20me%20because%20I%20am%20in%20a%20married%20life%20with%20you%26quot%3B%20when%20in%20fact%2C%20he%20is%20married%20to%20someone%20else%2C%20which%20is%20an%20offence%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Mr%20Gonsalves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20rise%20in%20allegations%20of%20inter-faith%20relationships%20in%20which%20the%20girl%20has%20exposed%20her%20husband%20as%20someone%20who%20lied%20and%20trapped%20her%20into%20marriage.%20It's%20a%20reality%20that%20the%20social%20context%20is%20changing%20in%20our%20country.%20It%20is%20imperative%20to%20amend%20laws%20and%20even%20bring%20in%20new%20legislation%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20changed%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20legal%20framework%20tackles%20%26quot%3Bcheating%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbreach%20of%20trust%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20new%20legislation%20will%20add%20more%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700745660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2Fnjd9j08o_wedding-generic_625x300_18_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwill-proposed-criminal-laws-curb-marriages-through-deceit-4600106%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20bills%20to%20replace%20British-era%20criminal%20laws%20were%20adopted%20recently%20by%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Home%20Affairs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwill-proposed-criminal-laws-curb-marriages-through-deceit-4600106%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwill-proposed-criminal-laws-curb-marriages-through-deceit-4600106%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwill-proposed-criminal-laws-curb-marriages-through-deceit-4600106%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22States%20Lacked%20Capacity%20to%20Test%20Fortified%20Rice%2C%20But%20Had%20to%20Give%20it%20to%20the%20Poor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161436%2FScreen-Shot-2023-11-20-at-5.25.58-PM-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EIndia%20is%20among%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20top%20food%20producers%3B%20yet%2C%20it%20faces%20a%20chronic%20undernourishment%20crisis%20with%2016%25%20of%20its%20population%20malnourished%20compared%20to%20the%20global%20average%20of%208%25.%20This%20three-part%20investigation%20traces%20the%20structural%20causes%20of%20hunger%20and%20food%20insecurity%20in%20inequalities%20in%20power%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20policy%20of%20rice%20fortification%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20public-sector%20food%20programmes.%20It%20examines%20the%20solutions%20the%20state%20is%20offering%20to%20ask%20what%20their%20true%20meaning%20is%20for%20people%20and%20the%20climate.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20mandatory%20rice%20fortification%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20public-sector%20food%20programmes%2C%20identifies%20the%20gaps%20in%20quality%20control.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3EState%20governments%20were%20given%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20switch%20to%20distributing%20chemically-fortified%20rice%2C%20even%20where%20infrastructure%20for%20quality%20was%20absent%2C%20or%20far%20from%20assured.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EIn%20villages%2C%20even%20those%20who%20question%20the%20policy%20are%20told%20to%20eat%20the%20new%20rice%2C%20artificially%20fortified%20with%20factory-made%20micronutrients.%20Adivasi%20farmers%20who%20have%20the%20knowledge%20and%20practice%20of%20growing%20a%20variety%20of%20rice%2C%20pulses%2C%20millets%2C%20and%20gathering%20tubers%2C%20small%20game%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20berries%20from%20the%20forest%20are%20further%20pushed%20to%20cereal-heavy%20diets%2C%20that%20have%20over%20time%20depleted%20soils%20and%20worsened%20nutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERead%20part%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fplastic-rice-why-union-govts-experiment-with-an-artificial-grain-is-hard-to-swallow-for-rural-adivasis%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERanchi%2FLatehar%20(Jharkhand)%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reduce%20anaemia%20and%20malnutrition%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20began%20experimenting%20with%20supplying%20rice%20grains%20artificially%20enhanced%20with%20micronutrients%20such%20as%20iron%2C%20vitamin%20B%2C%20folic%20acid%2C%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20in%202021.%20Medical%20experts%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS000291652200452X%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edebated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20benefits%20of%20chemically-fortified%20rice%20versus%20its%20potential%20harm.%20Public%20officials%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Ranchi%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20either%20distribute%20fortified%20rice%2C%20or%20forgo%20getting%20food%20aid%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERight%20to%20food%20and%20health%20activists%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkisanswaraj.in%2F2022%2F07%2F04%2Fjharkhand-government-must-stop-government-of-indias-misadventure-with-rice-fortification-state-goverment-should-not-distribute-fortified-rice-in-the-state-and-should-instea%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20documented%20concerns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20by%20forcing%20mandatory%20consumption%20of%20grains%20fortified%20with%20industry-made%20micronutrients%20in%20haste%2C%20the%20government%20has%20ignored%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20some%20of%20most%20vulnerable%20individuals%20who%20would%20consume%20this%20rice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20number%20of%20studies%20show%20the%20Union%20government%20released%20fortified%20rice%20to%20the%20public%20even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20serious%20gaps%20in%20infrastructure%20to%20assure%20quality.%20An%20evaluation%20of%20the%20scheme%20by%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20planning%20body%2C%20after%20visits%20to%20seven%20states%20showed%20the%20government%20proceeded%20even%20when%20laboratory%20facilities%20for%20ensuring%20basic%20quality%20in%20the%20supplied%20grains%20were%20lacking.%20As%20explained%20below%2C%20studies%20by%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme%20of%20the%20UN%2C%20and%20J-PAL%2C%20a%20global%20research%20centre%2C%20too%20showed%20similar%20gaps.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESetting%20sensitive%20standards%20on%20the%20go%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20fortify%20rice%20with%20factory-made%20nutrients%2C%20a%20powder%20%E2%80%9Cpre-mix%E2%80%9D%20of%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20%E2%80%93%20iron%2C%20vitamin%20B12%2C%20folic%20acid%20%E2%80%93%20is%20added%20to%20powdered%20rice%20and%20broken%20grains.%20The%20paste%20is%20machine-carved%20to%20manufacture%20new%20rice%20grains%2C%20which%20are%20mixed%20into%20grains%20being%20given%20as%20food%20rations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20in%20phase%20two%20of%20the%20programme%20when%20the%20government%20decided%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20pilots%20for%20fortified%20rice%20from%2015%20districts%20to%20291%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20up%20from%20providing%2035%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20to%20175%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20in%20social%20schemes%20%E2%80%93%20its%20coverage%20expanded%20quite%20rapidly%20in%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20all%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%2024%20districts%20are%20in%20the%20category%20%E2%80%9Caspirational%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20means%20they%20are%20extremely%20poor%20and%20are%20lacking%20in%20basic%20infrastructure%2C%20or%20they%20fall%20under%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20burden%E2%80%9D%20category%20of%20malnutrition%20and%20anemia.%20On%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20became%20evident%20that%20the%20haste%20in%20expanding%20the%20schemes%20led%20to%20lapses%20in%20accounting%20for%20quality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.49.21.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.49.21.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.49.21-300x219.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155019%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.49.21-1024x747.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686083%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22875%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENearly%20all%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Adivasi%20and%20rural%20poor%20live%20in%20districts%20in%20the%20category%20of%20%E2%80%9Caspirational%E2%80%9D%20or%20the%20poorest%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20a%20high%20burden%20on%20undernutrition.%C2%A0Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20statutory%20food%20regulator%2C%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Ffssai-to-roll-out-e-inspection-of-high-risk-food-businesses-11651598440123.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplaced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20category%20of%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20risk%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20require%20mandatory%20safety%20checks.%20Making%20chemically%20fortified%20rice%20requires%20regular%20monitoring.%20Measures%20include%20checking%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20powder%20pre-mix%20of%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20which%20is%20added%20into%20powdered%20rice%2C%20whether%20the%20micro-nutrients%20are%20as%20per%20the%20required%20Recommended%20Dietary%20Allowances%20(RDA)%20decided%20in%20scheme%20norms%2C%20if%20fortified%20rice%20was%20blended%20in%20the%20required%20proportions%20as%20stipulated%20(one%20enhanced%20or%20fortified%20grain%20to%20every%20100%20ordinary%20rice%20grains)%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20whether%20the%20rice%20gets%20eaten%20within%20its%20shelf-life%20period%20of%20one%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20lacks%20the%20required%20laboratories%20with%20facilities%20to%20check%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20pre-mix%20of%20micronutrients%20such%20as%20iron%2C%20folic%20acid%20and%20vitamins.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1mFv6mr6u8Ez49cXutA9gphW-07yviu2W%2Fview%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econfidential%20scheme%20evaluation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20May%202022%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20planning%20body%2C%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20first%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20flagged%20this%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20the%20laboratories%20that%20are%20accredited%20by%20the%20commerce%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20National%20Accreditation%20Board%20Testing%20and%20Calibration%20Laboratory%20(NABL)%20are%20equipped%20to%20accurately%20test%20micronutrient%20levels%20in%20the%20fortified%20rice%20kernels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20assessment%20of%20laboratory%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20it%20calculated%20using%20the%20number%20of%20samples%20that%20can%20be%20tested%20in%20a%20year%2C%20found%20a%20testing%20capacity%20of%202%2C66%2C333%20samples%20a%20year.%20It%20noted%20that%20when%20the%20scheme%20will%20be%20fully%20scaled%20up%20by%20March%202024%2C%20it%20will%20require%20testing%20nearly%209-10%20times%20more%2C%20at%2023%2C66%2C178%20samples.%20Thus%2C%20it%20estimated%20a%20gap%20of%2020%2C99%2C845%2C%20or%20nearly%20two%20million%20samples%2C%20indicating%20a%20huge%20mismatch%20between%20testing%20capacity%20and%20need%20that%20such%20a%20scheme%20entails.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20Union%20government%20pushed%20to%20expand%20the%20scheme%20rapidly%2C%20a%20state%20such%20as%20Jharkhand%2C%20in%20the%20interior%20eastern%20part%20of%20India%2C%20faced%20particular%20disadvantages.%20Though%20it%20has%20high%20numbers%20of%20those%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthiscorrespondence.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F10%2F17%2F60%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewho%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20depend%20on%20subsidised%20food%20rations%20%E2%80%93%2086%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20residents%20qualify%20for%20the%20food-grains%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20high%20number%20of%20ration%20outlets%2C%20it%20lacks%20even%20a%20single%20laboratory%20fully%20equipped%20to%20provide%20the%20quality%20checks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20east%20and%20the%20northeast%20region%2C%20where%20Jharkhand%20lies%2C%20has%20only%2010%25%20of%20the%20laboratories%20but%20holds%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20the%20food%20ration%20outlets%20and%20thus%20generates%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20samples%20for%20testing.%20But%20the%20laboratories%20are%20located%20primarily%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20northern%20region%20around%20the%20capital%2C%20or%20the%20south.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155425%2F1.2-NITI-Chart.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22757%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155425%2F1.2-NITI-Chart.png%20757w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155425%2F1.2-NITI-Chart-300x200.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686085%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENITI%20Ayog%20evaluation%20stated%20the%20East%20and%20North-East%20region%20have%20highest%20number%20of%20ration%20outlets%20%E2%80%93%20a%20high%20proportion%20of%20the%20rural%20residents%20survive%20on%20food%20subsidies%20%E2%80%93%20but%20few%20laboratories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20FSSAI%2C%20of%20the%20laboratories%20in%20India%20that%20can%20perform%20these%20tests%2C%20none%20are%20in%20Jharkhand.%20The%20closest%20such%20laboratory%20is%20in%20Kolkata%20in%20the%20adjoining%20state%20of%20Bengal.%20Yet%2C%20the%20evidence%20in%20Jharkhand%20shows%20the%20Union%20government%20proceeded%20with%20the%20compulsory%20scheme%20without%20ensuring%20the%20mechanism%20to%20timely%20verify%20the%20quality%20of%20and%20level%20of%20safe%20micronutrients%20fortified%20grains%20was%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20more%20than%20a%20year%20between%202021%20and%20early%202023%2C%20officials%20state%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20state%20government%20supplied%2056%2C000%20quintals%20of%20fortified%20rice%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20poorest.%20The%20micronutrient%20levels%20and%20quality%20of%20rice%20kernels%20was%20tested%20at%20Sun-Tech%2C%20the%20only%20NABL-laboratory%20located%20in%20Tupudana%2C%20Ranchi%2C%20in%20the%20state%20capital.%20However%2C%20this%20stopped%20earlier%20this%20year%20as%20the%20FSSAI%20stated%20that%20this%20laboratory%20cannot%20test%20micronutrients%20and%20it%20lacks%20the%20%E2%80%9CProficiency%20Test%E2%80%9D%20certification.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20one%20such%20laboratory%20in%20our%20state.%20But%20even%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20functional%20to%20test%20micronutrient%20levels%20in%20Fortified%20Rice%20Kernels%20(FRK)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yatinder%20Prasad%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20State%20Food%20Corporation%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%E2%80%99s%20secretary%20for%20food%20and%20civil%20supplies%20Amitabh%20Kaushal%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20callous%20path%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20guidelines%2C%20the%20FSSAI%20has%20to%20ensure%20NABL%20laboratories%20in%20all%20states%2C%20and%20periodically%20evaluate%20the%20scheme%20with%20the%20health%20ministry.%20On%20%E2%80%9Cquality%20assurance%20mechanisms%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20guidelines%20state%20%E2%80%9Can%20officer%20will%20verify%20Certificate%20of%20Analysis%20(proof%20of%20micronutrients%20analysis)%20of%20every%20fortified%20rice%20kernel(FRK)%20batch%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20sample%20is%20to%20be%20lifted%20from%20each%20blending%20point%20monthly%20to%20go%20to%20a%20NABL%20laboratory.%E2%80%9D%20It%20recommends%20that%20a%20sample%20of%20the%20fortified%20rice%20being%20distributed%20be%20collected%20monthly%20from%20the%20ration%20shop%2C%20or%20places%20it%20was%20served.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficials%20in%20Jharkhand%20said%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20collect%20and%20test%20samples%20from%20ration%20shops%2C%20schools%20and%20creches%2C%20and%20they%20believed%20that%20leaving%20it%20to%20manufacturers%20to%20prove%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20through%20such%20certificates%20of%20analyses%20may%20be%20inadequate%20to%20monitor%20in%20a%20foolproof%20way.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20lack%20such%20a%20laboratory%20in%20our%20state.%20And%20second%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20for%20us%20to%20get%20the%20micronutrients%E2%80%99%20tested%20in%20time%20for%20distributing%20the%20grains%20to%20poor%20households%20every%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20official.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20local%20authority%20overseeing%20this%20scheme%2C%20ideally%2C%20we%20prefer%20we%20should%20have%20had%20a%20second%20layer%20of%20testing%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20verify%20that%20no%20manipulation%20in%20quality%20was%20done%20by%20the%20rice%20kernel%20manufacturers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faahar.jharkhand.gov.in%2Fsecc-districts%2Fdistricts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprovides%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20food%20subsidies%20to%20more%20than%20six%20million%20poor%20households%2C%20or%20over%2026%20million%20residents.%20They%20are%20in%20two%20categories%3A%20priority%20households%20get%205%20kg%20rice%20per%20person%20per%20month%20and%20%E2%80%9CAntyodaya%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20poorest%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20are%20entitled%20to%2035%20kg%20per%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20430px)%2085vw%2C%20430px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155558%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.55.13.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22430%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155558%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.55.13.png%20982w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155558%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.55.13-298x300.png%20298w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23155558%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-3.55.13-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDasiya%20Parhaiyan%2C%20of%20a%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group%2C%20in%20Jharkhand%20attending%20a%20public%20hearing%20on%20barriers%20to%20right%20to%20food.%20Nearly%2086%25%20rural%20residents%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20poor%20residents%20survive%20on%20food%20subsidies.%20Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20laboratory%20takes%2010-15%20days%20to%20give%20us%20the%20results%20and%20if%20we%20wait%20that%20long%2C%20we%20cannot%20do%20the%20ration%20distribution%20by%20a%20fixed%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20explained%20the%20official.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20time%20to%20lift%20grains%20from%20the%20public%20system%20is%20fixed%2C%20or%20else%20the%20state%20would%20lose%20its%20quota%20of%20grains%2C%20and%20distribution%20is%20also%20time-bound.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20do%20it%20within%20a%20certain%20time%2C%20the%20Point%20of%20Sale%20devices%20at%20the%20retail%20stores%20will%20automatically%20block%20the%20disbursal%20of%20grains.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20official%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20infrastructure%20that%20should%20have%20been%20there%20for%20a%20scheme%20like%20this%20that%20affects%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20vital%20nutrition%20is%20absent.%20It%20is%20just%20not%20sufficient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20confidential%20NITI%20Aayog%20report%20drafted%20after%20visits%20to%20seven%20pilot%20districts%20documented%20serious%20lapses%20in%20quality%20control%2C%20and%20abdication%20of%20quality%20mechanisms%20by%20the%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20the%20substantial%20role%20envisioned%20in%20food%20ministry%20guidelines%20on%20the%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%9CFSSAI%20is%20found%20to%20have%20almost%20no%20role%20in%20quality%20assurance%2Fquality%20control%20of%20fortified%20rice%20within%20the%20visited%20districts%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20noted%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20no%20reported%20processes%20to%20monitor%20the%20quality%20and%20cost%20of%20the%20nutrient%20premix%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20found%20that%20in%20some%20districts%2C%20regular%20monitoring%20was%20by%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%20partners%E2%80%9D%2C%20such%20as%20Tata%20Trusts%2C%20or%20the%20American%20NGO%2C%20PATH.%20Though%20the%20guidelines%20state%20sample%20checking%20will%20be%20done%20at%20rice%20mills%2C%20FRK%20%5Bfortified%20rice%20kernel%5D%20plants%20and%20at%20ration%20shops%2C%20it%20found%20%E2%80%9Cno%20samples%20were%20being%20taken%20from%20rice%20mills%2C%20ration%20shops%20and%20children%E2%80%99s%20schools%20and%20creches%20where%20this%20was%20being%20served%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20officials%20from%20the%20food%20safety%20body%20and%20food%20and%20civil%20supplies%20department%20are%20supposed%20to%20independently%20test%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20FRK.%20In%20Jamshedpur%2C%20East%20Singhbhum%20district%2C%20supply%20officer%20Rajeev%20Ranjan%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20quality%20checks%20at%20mills%20were%20done%20by%20PATH%20in%20Jharkhand.%20PATH%20checked%20if%20the%20rice%20mills%20had%20obtained%20quality%20certificates%20when%20buying%20FRK%20from%20manufacturers%2C%20and%20if%20the%20tested%20and%20certified%20batch%20matched%20what%20was%20being%20provided%20further.%20For%20FRK%2C%20the%20manufacturers%20have%20to%20test%20every%20batch%20of%2010%20lakh%20metric%20tonne%2C%20and%20then%20PATH%20was%20trying%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20sample%20and%20final%20delivery%20batch%20of%20rice%20matched%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20called%20the%20mobile%20phone%20number%20listed%20on%20the%20internet%20by%20Sun-Tech%20Laboratory%20%E2%80%93%20the%20only%20nationally-accredited%20laboratory%20in%20Jharkhand%20which%20tested%20fortified%20rice%20in%202021-22%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20Shubham%20Mishra%2C%20a%20founding%20associate%20of%20the%20company%2C%20answered%20the%20call.%20He%20said%20he%20looked%20after%20the%20food%20division%20work%20done%20by%20the%20laboratory%20remotely%20from%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20had%20earlier%20worked%20from%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMishra%20said%20that%20Sun-Tech%20was%20among%2027%20of%2041%20NABL%20laboratories%20that%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cput%20on%20hold%E2%80%9D%20for%20testing%20fortified%20rice%20by%20the%20central%20food%20safety%20authorities%20as%20it%20failed%20to%20clear%20a%20%E2%80%9Cproficiency%20test%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2041%20labs%20were%20approved%20by%20FSSAI.%20Then%20FSSAI%20changed%20the%20method%20of%20technology%20of%20testing%20for%20micronutrient%20levels.%20Of%20those%2041%20labs%2C%2027%20were%20no%20longer%20considered%20qualified%20in%20a%20proficiency%20test.%20We%20were%20among%20those%20who%20did%20not%20qualify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20proper%20laboratory%20infrastructure%20was%20missing%2C%2056%2C000%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Equintals%20of%20fortified%20rice%20were%20supplied%20to%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20rural%20residents%20till%20June%202023.%20The%20supply%20of%20fortified%20rice%20went%20on%20even%20while%20the%20facilities%20to%20the%20test%20of%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20micronutrients%20being%20added%20were%20inadequate%2C%20or%20absent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMishra%2C%20from%20the%20Sun-Tech%20laboratory%2C%20accepted%20that%20testing%20micronutrient%20levels%20had%20been%20challenging%20for%20laboratories%20such%20as%20theirs.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20same%20sample%20of%20fortified%20rice%20gives%20different%20results%20when%20sent%20to%20test%20in%20different%20laboratories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20if%20we%20find%20a%20sample%20does%20not%20contain%20the%20required%20amount%20of%20micronutrients%2C%20iron%20and%20vitamin%20B12%20and%20it%20fails%2C%20when%20we%20send%20it%20to%20a%20different%20laboratory%20to%20compare%2C%20it%20fails%20the%20test%20not%20because%20it%20is%20too%20low%2C%20but%20instead%20because%20it%20exceeded%20the%20levels%20of%20micronutrients!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160011%2F3-rice-appearances.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160011%2F3-rice-appearances.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160011%2F3-rice-appearances-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160011%2F3-rice-appearances-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686088%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20fortified%20rice%20grains%20made%20in%20a%20factory%20are%20mixed%20in%20the%20ratio%201%3A100%20with%20natural%20rice%20grains%20and%20subjected%20to%20quality%20tests.%20They%20have%20a%20distinct%20artificial%20appearance.%C2%A0Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20problem%20had%20been%20identified%20during%20the%20pilots%20by%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%2C%20Sudhanshu%20Pandey.%20Speaking%20at%20a%20seminar%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20October%2025%2C%202021%2C%20Pandey%20said%20that%20his%20team%20had%20found%20that%20the%20laboratory%20infrastructure%20was%20not%20ready.%20He%20said%20that%20when%20they%20selected%20samples%20from%20various%20sites%2C%20the%20same%20sample%E2%80%99s%20results%20from%20two%20different%20laboratories%20were%20different%2C%20because%20the%20tests%20and%20equipment%20protocols%2C%20the%20laboratory%20machines%20were%20missing%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMishra%20of%20Sun-Tech%20laboratory%20said%20that%20the%20results%20of%20micronutrients%20in%20the%20fortified%20rice%20varied%20also%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20uniform%20blending%20by%20those%20who%20sold%20the%20fortified%20kernels%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20range%20of%20suppliers%20from%20big%20industry%20to%20smaller%20players.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESushil%20Sharma%2C%20owner%20of%20NuVit%20Foods%20FRK%2C%20a%20small%20newly-established%20factory%20near%20Jamshedpur%20said%20the%20price%20range%20and%20quality%20of%20of%20pre-mix%20he%20had%20purchased%20to%20supply%20into%20Jharkhand%20ration%20supply%20varied%20from%20Rs%20240%20to%20Rs%20320%20per%20kilo.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExact%20blending%20in%20fortified%20rice%20to%20natural%20rice%20grains%20in%20a%20ratio%20of%201%3A100%20grains%20required%20costly%20blending%20equipment%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20said%20Abhishek%20Jain%2C%20who%20is%20a%20production%20manager%20at%20JVS%20Foods%20Pvt%20Limited%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20and%20largest%20supplier%20of%20fortified%20kernels.%20%E2%80%9CSmaller%20manufacturers%20prefer%20to%20use%20cheaper%20pre-mix%2C%20and%20equipment%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%202-3%20lakh%2C%20which%20does%20not%20ensure%20proper%20blending%E2%80%9D%2C%20claimed%20Jain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20partnered%20with%20educational%20institutes%20to%20create%20and%20set%20standards%20for%20blending%20machines%2C%20but%20these%20remained%20costly%20and%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20small%2C%20local%20rice%20mills%2C%20acknowledged%20state%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Jharkhand%20food%20department%20first%20started%20supplying%20fortified%20rice%2C%20it%20had%20identified%20Jain%E2%80%99s%20factory%20in%20Jaipur%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%201%2C300%20kilometres%20from%20Ranchi%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20qualified%20suppliers.%20In%202022%2C%20it%20asked%20mills%20to%20procure%20the%20grains%20from%20NuVit%20Foods%20in%20East%20Singhbhum.%20This%20year%2C%20it%20had%20identified%20three%20kernel%20manufacturers%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Guwahati%2C%20Kolkata%20as%20qualified%20suppliers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJain%20of%20JVS%20Foods%20described%20the%20proliferation%20of%20fortified%20rice%20kernel%20manufacturers%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20since%20the%20union%20government%20announced%20the%20scheme%20as%20one%20of%20the%20causes%20of%20poor%20quality%20fortification%20going%20on%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20more%20than%20600%20fortified%20rice%20kernel%20makers%20have%20come%20up.%20Of%20these%2C%20hardly%2060%20large%20players%20like%20us%20sell%20quality%20kernels%20with%20the%20right%20level%20of%20micronutrients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jain%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eat%20his%20factory%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20supply%20it%20into%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%2C%20rice%20mill%20owners%20have%20to%20order%20and%20purchase%20of%20fortified%20rice%20kernels%2C%20blend%20it%20into%20ration%20rice%2C%20and%20the%20government%20reimburses%20them%20later.%20Jain%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20cases%2C%20small%20rice%20millers%20have%20started%20making%20the%20fortified%20rice%20kernels%2C%20thinking%20that%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20big%20issue%3F%20We%20will%20just%20install%20an%20extruder%20machine%20and%20make%20FRK%20ourselves%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20add%20low%20quality%20pre-mix%2C%20or%20they%20purchase%20from%20a%20large%20company%20such%20as%20Royal%20DSM%20(the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20vitamin%20maker%2C%20a%20Dutch%20firm%20which%20JVS%20purchases%20premixes%20from)%2C%20but%20then%20they%20blend%20in%20additional%20material%20of%20sub-%20standard%20quality%2C%20to%20increase%20the%20volume.%20But%20the%20quality%20is%20zero.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20437px)%2085vw%2C%20437px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160232%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.01.50.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22437%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160232%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.01.50.png%20912w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160232%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.01.50-228x300.png%20228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160232%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.01.50-778x1024.png%20778w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686090%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMore%20than%205%2C000%20millers%20in%20Punjab%20went%20on%20a%20strike%20in%20October%20over%20the%20issues%20they%20are%20facing%20in%20sourcing%20fortified%20rice.%20There%20is%20inadequate%20quality%20control%20of%20fortified%20rice.%20Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issues%20of%20quality%2C%20of%20unreliable%20laboratory%20results%20of%20micronutrients%20have%20continued.%20Last%20month%2C%20over%205%2C500%20rice%20millers%20that%20process%20rice%20to%20supply%20as%20rations%20to%20the%20Punjab%20government%20went%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fonly-34-of-paddy-lifted-as-millers-strike-continues-against-fci-guidelines-101697399269238.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20strike%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20October%2013%20throwing%20the%20paddy%20procurement%20into%20chaos.%20The%20central%20government%20bodies%20had%20rejected%20the%20rice%20they%20had%20blended%20fortified%20kernels%20as%20lacking%20iron%20and%20vitamins%20as%20per%20the%20scheme%20norms.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20sometimes%20a%20200%25%20difference%20in%20results%20of%20micronutrients%20tests%20from%20one%20laboratory%20to%20another%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tarsem%20Lal%20Saini%2C%20president%20of%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20rice%20millers%20association%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20is%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20monitoring%20of%20laboratories%20and%20quality%20aspects.%20How%20can%20we%20be%20held%20responsible%20if%20the%20right%20systems%20for%20assuring%20quality%20are%20not%20in%20place%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFSSAI%20officials%2C%20whose%20role%20it%20is%20to%20regulate%20these%20quality%20aspects%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20request%20for%20comment%20and%20to%20right%20to%20information%20queries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EStudies%20found%20serious%20gaps%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WFP%2C%20which%20worked%20with%20the%20FSSAI%2C%20evaluated%20the%20scheme%20pilots%20too%20and%20highlighted%20serious%20gaps%20in%20quality%20control%20and%20monitoring.%20Its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F13ma1qijGsp0OUIMNetJgHRcYtHzjTs0W%2Fview%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eevaluation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20called%20%E2%80%9CStatus%20Update%E2%80%9D%20of%20April%202021%20documented%20findings%20from%20several%20states.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Assam%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20it%20mentioned%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20progress%E2%80%9D%20in%20quality%20control%2C%20for%20Chhattisgarh%20it%20states%20that%20it%20does%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20have%20a%20NABL%20accredited%20laboratory%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Cno%20defined%20mechanism%20of%20monitoring%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmillers%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20FRK%20suppliers%20on%20their%20own.%20This%20may%20lead%20to%20compromise%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20FRK%20and%20fortified%20rice.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Jharkhand%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20even%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20it%20found%2C%20%E2%80%9Cno%20baseline%20for%20scheme%20conducted%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20the%20WFP%20found%20%E2%80%9CLack%20of%20compliance%20towards%20Quality%20control%2FQuality%20Assurance%20in%20FRK%20production%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20absence%20of%20regular%2C%20well%20defined%20monitoring%20mechanism%20by%20department%2Fgovernment%20officers%2C%20rice%20millers%20are%20not%20able%20to%20enforce%20regular%20checks%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20more%20seriously%2C%20that%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20stabilisation%20and%20variation%20in%20result%20of%20micronutrient%20analysis%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20But%20even%20after%20flagging%20these%20serious%20lacunae%2C%20including%20in%20absence%20of%20quality%20control%20mechanisms%20in%20this%20food%20intervention%2C%20the%20WFP%20report%20went%20on%20to%20recommend%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%9Cscale%20up%20the%20distribution%20of%20fortified%20rice%E2%80%9D%20in%20all%20public%20schemes%20for%20children%E2%80%99s%20nutrition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160352%2F4.1-WFP-identified-challenges-the-quality-control-in-several-states-yet-recommended-scaling-up.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22822%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160352%2F4.1-WFP-identified-challenges-the-quality-control-in-several-states-yet-recommended-scaling-up.png%20822w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160352%2F4.1-WFP-identified-challenges-the-quality-control-in-several-states-yet-recommended-scaling-up-300x106.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686092%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22290%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWFP%20evaluation%20in%2015%20states%20found%20serious%20gaps%20in%20quality%20control%2C%20but%20it%20still%20recommended%20scaling%20up%20even%20as%20infrastructure%20was%20not%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20pilot%20study%20conducted%20by%20J-PAL%2C%20a%20research%20centre%2C%20similarly%20cautioned%20against%20lack%20of%20readiness%20and%20of%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20intervention.%20J-PAL%E2%80%99s%20large%20scale%20pilot%20in%20Cuddalore%20district%20with%20government%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20a%20cluster%20randomised%20control%20trial%2C%20which%20would%20compare%20the%20results%20between%20a%20population%20not%20eating%20fortified%20rice%20with%20a%20group%20that%20was%20given%20rice%20fortified%20with%20iron%2C%20zinc%2C%20Vitamin%20A%2C%20B%20%E2%80%9Cat%20levels%20recommended%20by%20WFP%E2%80%9D.%20The%20project%20was%20discontinued%20in%202020%20and%20its%20authors%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20international%20academics%2C%20listed%20five%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20challenges%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20government%2C%20and%20highlighted%20the%20absence%20of%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20stated%20that%20in%20India%2C%20the%20technology%20to%20produce%20fortified%20rice%20kernels%20or%20FRK%20of%20adequate%20quality%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20and%20still%20is%20in%20infancy%E2%80%9D%2C%20further%20that%20these%20%E2%80%9Csubpar%20products%20are%20not%20accepted%20by%20consumers%20and%20may%20not%20withstand%20normal%20cooking%20processes%20which%20may%20cause%20loss%20of%20micronutrients.%E2%80%9D%20They%20pointed%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20clear%20and%20widely%20shared%20test%20protocols%20to%20test%20micronutrient%20content.%20They%20said%20that%20measuring%20water-soluble%20vitamins%20was%20especially%20hard%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Csome%20laboratories%20do%20not%20deliver%20consistent%20reliable%20measurements%20despite%20being%20certified%2C%20leading%20to%20delays%20and%20uncertainty.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20they%20stated%20that%20their%20study%20had%20used%20micronutrient%20levels%20as%20per%20the%20WFP%3B%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20FSSAI%20guidelines%20allow%20for%20lower%20(but%20possibly%20less%20effective)%20micronutrient%20content%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160455%2F4.2-JPAL-challenges.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22876%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160455%2F4.2-JPAL-challenges.png%20876w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160455%2F4.2-JPAL-challenges-300x145.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686093%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22424%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20note%20by%20a%20team%20of%20global%20researchers%20listed%20key%20challenges%20they%20faced%20while%20trying%20to%20study%20if%20rice%20fortification%20in%20the%20PDS%20reduced%20anaemia%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Cuddalore%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20one%20hand%2C%20thus%2C%20there%20were%20unresolved%20questions%20by%20scientists%20and%20medical%20experts%20who%20have%20been%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20regulatory%20panel%20on%20over-layering%20with%20iron%20for%20certain%20vulnerable%20groups%20with%20medical%20conditions%20such%20as%20sickle%20cell%20disease%2C%20malaria%20or%20thalassemia%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fplastic-rice-why-union-govts-experiment-with-an-artificial-grain-is-hard-to-swallow-for-rural-adivasis%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20explained%20in%20part%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20series%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20On%20the%20other%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20trials%20on%20the%20intervention%20had%20been%20discontinued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedical%20experts%20and%20scientists%20say%20that%20the%20researchers%E2%80%99%20note%20raises%20a%20question%20on%20the%20logic%20and%20efficacy%20of%20micro-dosing%20anemic%20individuals%20with%20small%20quantities%20of%20iron.%20Crucially%2C%20there%20is%20the%20vital%20question%20about%20local%20food%20alternatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20range%20of%20iron%20as%20per%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20rules%20should%20be%2028%20to%2042.5%20milligrams%20per%20100%20grams%20for%20iron%20content.%20Researchers%20as%20well%20as%20farm%20activists%20pointed%20out%20that%20more%20nutritious%2C%20far%20richer%20in%20iron%20indigenous%20or%20folk%20rice%20varieties%20are%20cultivated%20by%20farmers%20in%20India.%20Dr%20Debal%20Deb%2C%20a%20plant%20scientist%20and%20paddy%20conservator%20in%20Odisha%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20has%20identified%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20varieties%20of%20Indian%20rice%2C%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDudhe%20Bolta%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(130%20mg%20per%20kg)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBhuri%20Shulah%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(85%20mg%20per%20kg)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELeda%20Sal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(65%20mg%20per%20kg)%2C%20which%20have%20a%20much%20higher%20content%20of%20iron%20naturally%2C%20between%2010%20to%20152%20mg%20per%20kg%2C%20than%20the%20content%20of%20the%20iron%20in%20the%20factory-made%20fortified%20rice%20kernels.%20Dr%20Deb%20has%20published%20these%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.academia.edu%2F96317089%2FA_profile_of_heavy_metals_in_rice_Oryza_sativa_ssp_indica_landraces%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efindings%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20journals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160730%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.06.28.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160730%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.06.28.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160730%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.06.28-300x161.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160730%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.06.28-1024x550.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686094%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22645%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20forests%20and%20farmlands%20of%20this%20region%20support%20a%20varieties%20of%20rice%2C%20beans%2C%20lentils%2C%20millets%2C%20and%C2%A0%20forest%20foods.%C2%A0Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20agriculture%20department%20can%20help%20grow%20a%20variety%20of%20these%20native%2C%20nutritious%2C%20iron-rich%20rice%20varieties%20and%20make%20them%20available%20through%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%2C%E2%80%9Dsaid%20Dr%20Deb%20who%20has%20conserved%20more%20than%201%2C450%20native%20rice%20varieties%20in%20one%20of%20South%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20seed%20bank%20in%20Rayagada%20district%20in%20Odisha.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20each%20indigenous%20variety%20of%20rice%20is%20unique%2C%20and%20several%20are%20naturally%20rich%20in%20nutrients%20such%20as%20iron%2C%20zinc%2C%20antioxidants%2C%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20supporting%20this%20farming%2C%20the%20government%20has%20adopted%20a%20centralised%20policy%20pulverising%2C%20blending%2C%20re-moulding%20paste%20to%20look%20like%20rice%20grains.%20Such%20a%20policy%20is%20illogical%20and%20wastes%20public%20funds%2C%20it%20favours%20only%20big%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESmothering%20small%20businesses%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Chakulia%2C%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Crice%20bowl%E2%80%9D%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20sized%20rice%20mills%20enterprises%20were%20struggling%20with%20the%20financial%20implications%20of%20the%20switch%20to%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20social%20security%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20fortified%20rice%20supply%20chain%2C%20rice%20kernel%20manufacturing%20firms%20import%20the%20pre-mix%20containing%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20as%20micronutrients%20and%20add%20this%20to%20the%20rice%20paste%20to%20make%20artificial%20rice%20kernels%20using%20%E2%80%9Chot%20extrusion%E2%80%9D%20technology.%20The%20rice%20mill%20operators%20have%20to%20buy%20these%20kernels%20and%20blend%20them%20into%20custom%20milled%20rice%20very%20carefully%20in%20a%20ratio%20of%201%3A100%20%E2%80%93%20one%20chemically%20fortified%20kernel%20of%20rice%20to%20every%20100%20grains%20of%20rice%20%E2%80%93%20using%20blending%20machines.%20They%20transport%20this%20to%20government%E2%80%99s%20godowns%20from%20where%20it%20goes%20to%20retail%20outlets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20scheme%20norms%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20stated%20it%20would%20cover%20basic%20costs%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%2073%20for%20every%20quintal%20of%20fortified%20rice%20that%20the%20mills%20supply.%20But%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20it%20has%20not%20covered%20even%20this%20basic%20cost%20that%20small%20and%20medium%20millers%20bore.%20The%20millers%20too%20said%20that%20they%20were%20coerced%20to%20switch%20to%20the%20new%20system%2C%20or%20threatened%20with%20losing%20their%20licenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20April%202021%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20state%20government%20told%20us%20to%20switch%20to%20supplying%20fortified%20rice%2C%E2%80%9D%20recounted%20one%20rice%20mill%20owner.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%98To%20remain%20as%20a%20supplier%20of%20rice%20into%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20(PDS)%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20install%20machines%20which%20blend%20fortified%20rice%E2%80%99.%20The%20switch%20was%20done%20in%20such%20a%20hurry%2C%20almost%20overnight%2C%20that%20those%20who%20could%20not%20install%20or%20operate%20the%20blending%20machines%2C%20mixed%20the%20kernels%20into%20rice%20manually%2C%20by%20hand!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CUsually%20for%20milling%20for%20eg.%205%2C000%20quintals%20of%20paddy%20for%20the%20PDS%2C%20the%20government%20pays%20us%20Rs%201%20lakh%20as%20incentive.%20They%20forced%20us%20to%20install%20the%20machines%20by%20withholding%20our%20incentive%20payments%20in%202021.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160911%2F5-inside-mill.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160911%2F5-inside-mill.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160911%2F5-inside-mill-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160911%2F5-inside-mill-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686097%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EInside%20a%20rice%20mill%20in%20Chakulia%20in%20East%20Singhbhum%2C%20Jharkhand.%20Chakulia%20was%20chosen%20as%20a%20pilot%20block%20as%20most%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20rice%20mills%20are%20here.%20Photo%3A%20Manob%20Chowdhury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeepak%20Jhunjhunwala%2C%20who%20owns%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20mills%2C%20Maa%20Jagdambaa%20Udyog%2C%20in%20Chakulia%20and%20leads%20the%20Chakulia%20rice%20mill%20association%2C%20was%20among%20the%20four%20mill%20owners%20ordered%20to%20switch%20to%20supplying%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20pilot%20scheme.%20He%20estimates%20that%20he%20lost%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20lapsed%20incentive%20payments%20in%202021.%20This%20was%20after%20he%20had%20spent%20spending%20Rs%208%20lakh%20to%20install%20a%20blending%20machine%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20instruction%2C%20besides%20bearing%20the%20costs%20to%20hire%20staff%20to%20supervise%20the%20blending%20and%20paying%20for%20procuring%20and%20testing%20fortified%20rice%20between%202021-22.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedium%20and%20small%20businesses%20received%20no%20government%20support%20for%20their%20costs.%20Between%202021%20and%20November%202023%2C%20they%20had%20not%20even%20received%20any%20payments%20due%20for%20fortifying%20rice%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%2073%20per%20quintal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20not%20paid%20Rs%2034%2C20%2C835%20for%20the%20fortified%20rice%20he%20had%20supplied%20to%20the%20PDS%20from%20mid%202021%20till%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jhunjhunwala.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mill%20owners%20too%20had%20got%20quality%20of%20each%20batch%20of%20the%20fortified%20rice%20they%20supplied%20tested%20at%20Sun-Tech%20laboratory%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20till%20this%20year%20when%20the%20laboratory%20was%20taken%20off%20the%20FSSAI%20list%20of%20qualified%20laboratories%20to%20test%20micronutrients.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20mill-owners%20were%20asked%20to%20discontinue%20the%20testing%2C%20which%20would%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20kernel%20makers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20under%20the%20guidelines%2C%20the%20FSSAI%20is%20responsible%20for%20visiting%20the%20mills%20including%20for%20quality%20checks%2C%20none%20of%20the%20mill%20owners%20interviewed%20in%20Chakulia%20had%20had%20any%20quality%20check%20visits%20by%20the%20FSSAI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20time%20FSSAI%20staff%20visited%20us%20was%20to%20give%20us%20%E2%80%9CF%2B%E2%80%9D%20license%20in%20early%202023%2C%20after%20we%20had%20applied%20for%20a%20license%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20mill%20owner.%20This%20license%20denotes%20that%20the%20mill%20is%20qualified%20to%20sell%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20open%20market%2C%20outside%20the%20public%20distribution%20system.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20did%20not%20visit%20to%20inspect%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20milled%20rice%20otherwise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20entrepreneur%20who%20mills%20rice%20from%20paddy%20and%20sell%20to%20wholesalers%20who%20further%20sell%20to%20retail%20grocery%20shops%20said%20they%20found%20no%20demand%20from%20either%20individual%20consumers%2C%20or%20wholesalers%20for%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20market%2C%20outside%20the%20government%20public%20distribution%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwadeshi%20Jagran%20Manch%2C%20an%20economic%20wing%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsewak%20Sangh%2C%20which%20promotes%20domestic%20industry%20has%20questioned%20the%20effects%20of%20mandatory%20food%20fortification%20on%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20in%20India.%20In%20the%2090s%2C%20SJM%20had%20opposed%20mandatory%20fortification%20of%20salt%20with%20iodine%20and%20led%20a%20campaign%20to%20allow%20small%20enterprises%20to%20continue%20making%20common%20salt%2C%20without%20added%20iodine%2C%20available.%20%E2%80%9COnly%20very%20large%20industry%20is%20able%20to%20afford%20these%20standardisation%20and%20processing%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20SJM%20national%20co-convenor%20Ashwani%20Mahajan.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20revoked%20the%20mandatory%20fortifying%20with%20iodine%20and%20allowing%20making%20of%20common%20salt.%20Yet%2C%20small%20firms%20making%20salt%20were%20wiped%20out.%E2%80%9D%20Mahajan%20questioned%20why%20mandatory%20fortification%20was%20being%20imposed%20on%20small%20industry%20such%20as%20mills.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20was%20a%20proven%20matter%20of%20saving%20lives%2C%20then%20one%20can%20understand%20forcing%20this%20standardisation%20on%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20proven%20credibility%20in%20organisations%20pushing%20such%20interventions.%20Instead%2C%20there%20is%20evidence%20that%20artificial%20micronutrients%20cannot%20get%20assimilated%20into%20the%20body%20easily.%20We%20need%20nutrition%20from%20natural%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98It%20is%20nothing%20like%20rice%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chhotanagpur%20region%2C%20which%20parts%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Odisha%20fall%20in%2C%20is%20a%20forested%20region%20and%20holds%20biodiversity%20hotspots%20rich%20in%20indigenous%20millets%2C%20rice%20varieties%2C%20pulses%20and%20forest%20foods.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161056%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.10.24.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161056%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.10.24.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161056%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.10.24-300x185.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161056%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.10.24-1024x632.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686099%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22741%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20Oraon%20Adivasi%20in%20Latehar%2C%20Jharkhand%20gathering%20gethi%2C%20a%20tuber.%20Most%20Adivasi%20families%20cultivate%20small%20plots%20and%20also%20get%20tubers%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20berries%20from%20the%20forest.%20Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDayamani%20Barla%2C%20an%20Adivasi%20activist%20fighting%20to%20preserve%20indigenous%20communities%E2%80%99%20land%20and%20forest%20rights%20said%20the%20scheme%20had%20been%20implemented%20in%20haste%2C%20without%20consulting%20the%20communities%20who%20would%20have%20to%20eat%20the%20fortified%20rice%2C%20and%20without%20understanding%20their%20food%20systems%3A%20%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20farmers%20keep%20the%20paddy%20they%20grow%20in%20storage%20at%20homes%2C%20and%20when%20they%20have%20to%20eat%2C%20process%20a%20small%20quantity%20at%20home%20and%20eat%20it%20fresh.%20They%20eat%20parboiled%20rice%20and%20millets.%20They%20complement%20that%20with%20ration%20rice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeepak%20Pani%2C%20director%20of%20Gram%20Swaraj%2C%20a%20NGO%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Mayurbhanj%20district%2C%20which%20works%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20millets%20program%2C%20argued%20that%20even%20if%20the%20intention%20was%20to%20provide%20further%20nutrition%20with%20staples%20such%20as%20cereals%2C%20the%20union%20government%20ought%20to%20have%20seriously%20explored%20other%20food%20options.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20need%20for%20rice%20fortified%20with%20nutrition%20in%20factories%20when%20local%20rice%20varieties%20and%20millets%20contain%20more%20nutrients%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20%E2%80%9COn%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20government%20claims%20it%20is%20supporting%20local%20climate%20resilient%2C%20nutritious%20crops%20such%20as%20millets%2C%20on%20the%20other%2C%20it%20is%20making%20industrial%20food%20fortification%20compulsory.%20This%20is%20a%20contradiction%20in%20its%20approach.%20Unpolished%20rice%20varieties%20grown%20in%20villages%20here%20are%20far%20richer%20in%20nutrients.%E2%80%9D%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20millets%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20richer%20in%20micronutrients%20than%20fortified%20rice%20%E2%80%93%20if%20kept%20dry%2C%20could%20easily%20be%20stored%20for%20up%20to%2015%20years%20for%20use%20in%20public%20distribution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20villages%2C%20the%20picture%20is%20more%20complex.%20Smallholder%20farmers%20shared%20that%20with%20a%20slow%20but%20gradual%20process%20of%20ecological%20and%20cultural%20erosion%20in%20this%20biodiversity%20rich%20region%2C%20the%20soils%20in%20all%20areas%20now%20no%20longer%20support%20growing%20certain%20older%20folk%20varieties%20of%20cereals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Latehar%20district%2C%20which%20started%20getting%20fortified%20rice%20in%20phase%20two%20last%20year%2C%20farmers%20affirmed%20that%20since%2010-15%20years%20their%20%E2%80%9Cown%20paddy%20varieties%E2%80%9D%20(indigenous%20seeds)%20no%20longer%20grew%20well.%20They%20believed%20that%20this%20had%20happened%20after%20increasing%20fertiliser%20use.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20all%20our%20paddy%20seeds%20were%20our%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pravesh%20Oraon%2C%20the%20mukhiya%20headman%20of%20Khairajat%20a%20village%20by%20the%20foothills%2C%20though%20only%2020%20kilometers%20from%20the%20town%20of%20Latehar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20growing%20hybrid%20paddy%20varieties%2010%20years%20back.%20Within%20five%20years%20of%20using%20these%20with%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20our%20older%20paddy%20varieties%20now%20no%20longer%20grow%20on%20the%20same%20soil%20as%20they%20did%20earlier%20without%20fertilizers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20more%20remote%20village%20Chormunda%20in%20Mahuadanr%20block%20on%20top%20of%20the%20plateau%2C%20the%20commercial%20pady%20seeds%20had%20been%20slower%20to%20reach%2C%20and%20several%20smaller%20farmer%20still%20grow%20folk%20rice%20varieties.%20The%20area%20started%20getting%20fortified%20rice%20as%20rations%20only%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161221%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.11.48.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161221%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.11.48.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161221%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.11.48-300x198.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23161221%2FScreenshot-2023-11-23-at-4.11.48-1024x674.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686100%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22790%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECatherine%20Tithio%2C%20a%20farmer%20in%20Latehar%E2%80%99s%20Mahuadanr%20block%2C%20said%20she%20cultivated%202-3%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20rice%2C%20millets%2C%20potatoes%20and%20greens.%20Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%2C%20Catherine%20Tithio%20a%20tall%20gaunt%20Adivasi%20farmer%20was%20plucking%20mustard%20saplings%20that%20had%20sprouted%20in%20her%20fields%20after%20scattered%20showers.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGoda-dhan%2C%20Chosaarh%2C%20Kalamdaani%2C%20Ranikajar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20counted%20the%20indigenous%20rice%20varieties%20her%20family%20continued%20to%20plant%2C%20which%20grew%20without%20fertilisers%20or%20irrigation.%20Along%20with%20these%2C%20they%20grew%20little%20millets%20and%20potatoes%2C%20she%20said.%20Still%2C%20Tithio%20too%20said%20she%20did%20not%20trust%20the%20new%20fortified%20rice%20because%20of%20its%20appearance.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20heard%20that%20this%20is%20plastic.%20I%20cannot%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20looks%20different%20from%20our%20rice%2C%20and%20it%20does%20not%20look%20good.%20To%20be%20cautious%2C%20I%20separate%20it%20out%20while%20cooking.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20remote%20forest%20hamlets%20of%20Subdega%20block%20in%20Odisha%20district%20Sundargarh%2C%20Albisia%20Lakra%20a%20rice%20farmers%20she%20was%20not%20convinced%20that%20the%20rice%20was%20laden%20with%20vital%20nutrients.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20too%20white!%20It%20looks%20quite%20distinct.%20I%20separate%20it%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lakra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FMkz8JRVBltA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BPlastic%20Rice%26quot%3B%3A%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Experiment%20With%20Fortified%20Rice%20Hard%20to%20Swallow%20for%20India's%20Adivasi%20Residents%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20had%20dried%20various%20produce%20in%20her%20courtyard%20%E2%80%93%20yam%2C%20gourds%2C%20and%20berries%20%E2%80%93%20and%20had%20dried%20kulthi%20dal%2C%20horse%20gram%20lentils%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20her%20hut%20in%20Deogaon-Kalumara%20village.%20Lakra%20confirmed%20that%20the%20village%20health%20worker%2C%20the%20ASHA(Accredited%20Social%20Health%20Activist%20employed%20by%20health%20ministry)%20had%20informed%20the%20village%20residents%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cvitamin%20rice%E2%80%9D%20and%20instructed%20them%20to%20eat%20it%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20we%20wash%20the%20rice%20with%20warm%20water%2C%20boil%20it%20to%20cook%20the%20rice%2C%20rinse%20it%2C%20then%20anyway%20the%20water%20is%20washed%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lakra%2C%20as%20she%20separated%20the%20rice%20grains%20out%20on%20a%20sieve%2C%20distinct%20opaque%20factory-made%20grains%2C%20away%20from%20the%20bulk%20of%20grains%20it%20had%20been%20mixed%20into.%C2%A0%3C