F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fhealthcare%2Fbiotech%2Fpharmaceuticals%2Fdrug-regulator-halts-production-at-76-units-over-poor-standards%2Farticleshow%2F105425061.cms%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20poor%20manufacturing%20standards%20were%20discovered%20during%20risk-based%20inspections%20that%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20since%20December%2C%20people%20aware%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20cited%20data%20from%20the%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20(CDSCO)%2C%20saying%20that%20out%20of%20the%20237%20manufacturing%20units%20that%20have%20been%20inspected%20so%20far%2C%20179%20have%20been%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELicences%20of%2015%20firms%20have%20been%20cancelled%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2015%25%20of%20the%20total%20samples%20drawn%20from%20these%20manufacturing%20units%20have%20been%20declared%20to%20be%20not%20of%20standard%20quality.%20And%20therefore%2C%2035%20units%20have%20been%20sent%20warning%20letters%20for%20discrepancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20regulator%20is%20currently%20conducting%20Phase%20IV%20of%20these%20inspections%2C%20during%20which%2051%20pharma%20firms%20have%20been%20inspected%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Findia-wide-inspections-of-pharma-firms-exposed-major-lapses-in-drug-manufacturing-shows-govt-analysis-8673002.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENews18%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20common%20observations%20in%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20inspection%20were%20about%20%E2%80%9Cissues%20of%20data%20integrity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20found%20a%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20a%20dedicated%20section%20for%20potent%20products%E2%80%9D%20apart%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20vendor%20qualification%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20SOPs%20or%20failure%20to%20follow%20SOPs%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20freedom%20to%20the%20technical%20staff%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20news%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20in%20previous%20inspections%2C%20the%20common%20observations%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cfood%20supplements%20manufactured%20in%20the%20same%20premises%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20information%20was%20based%20on%20a%20presentation%20made%20by%20Chandrashekhar%20Ranga%2C%20deputy%20drugs%20controller%20of%20CDSCO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20presentation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Findia-wide-inspections-of-pharma-firms-exposed-major-lapses-in-drug-manufacturing-shows-govt-analysis-8673002.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENews18%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20one%20of%20the%20outcomes%20of%20risk-based%20inspections%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cregulators%20came%20to%20know%20the%20ground%20reality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20these%20inspections%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20CDSCO%20along%20with%20state%20drug%20inspectors%20after%20cough%20syrups%20manufactured%20in%20India%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fcough-syrup-india-gambia-deaths-children-who%5C%22%3Elinked%20to%20the%20deaths%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%2060%20children%20in%20Gambia.%20This%20incident%20sparked%20serious%20concerns%20over%20the%20quality%20of%20Indian%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20299%20firms%2C%20including%2072%20private%20testing%20laboratories%2C%20were%20inspected%20during%20the%20four%20phases%20of%20the%20risk-based%20inspections%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20labs%20are%20required%20to%20comply%20with%20good%20laboratory%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20July%2C%2072%20public%20testing%20labs%20have%20been%20audited.%20Of%20them%2C%2039%20were%20sent%20show%20cause%20notices%2C%20nine%20were%20issued%20orders%20to%20stop%20testing%2C%20and%20five%20were%20sent%20warning%20letters%2C%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20a%20total%20of%20218%20firms%20have%20been%20sent%20show%20cause%20notices%2C%2076%20(33%25)%20were%20issued%20stop%20manufacturing%20orders%2C%2015%20firms%20faced%20cancellation%20of%20licences%20and%2040%20were%20issued%20warning%20letters%2C%20people%20in%20the%20know%20told%3Cem%3E%20ET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENews18%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20inspection%20sites%20were%20selected%20based%20on%20six%20parameters%20%E2%80%93%20a%20national%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Biologics%20(NIB)%2C%20reports%20from%20the%20labs%20under%20CDSCO%2C%20reports%20from%20state%20labs%2C%20reports%20from%20international%20regulatory%20agencies%2C%20information%20gathered%20through%20intelligence%20and%20all%20130%20oxytocin%20injection%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Ranga%E2%80%99s%20presentation%2C%20the%20risk-based%20inspections%20conducted%20in%202016%20and%202022-2023%20showed%20that%20there%20are%20423%20sites%20with%20two%20or%20more%20failures%2C%20319%20sites%20with%20three%20or%20more%20failures%20and%20spurious%2C%20and%20100%20sites%20with%20five%20or%20more%20failures%20and%20spurious.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700723719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23115348%2Fimage-1528.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcdsco-halt-production-pharma-firms-poor-standards%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20(CDSCO)%20has%20also%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices%20to%20179%20of%20237%20manufacturing%20units%20that%20have%20been%20inspected%2C%20according%20to%20Economic%20Times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22