%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-3-1700576807-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sudhir%20Srivastava%20with%20his%20surgical%20robot%3B%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20SS%20Innovations%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20team%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20expanding%20and%20modifying%20a%20truck%20to%20accommodate%20the%20robotic%20system%20in%20it.%20The%20truck%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20conduct%20camps%20in%20the%20remotest%20areas%20of%20the%20country%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20journey%20so%20far%2C%20Dr%20Sudhir%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20had%20no%20money.%20Projects%20like%20these%20require%20millions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20investment%20while%20I%20was%20there%20with%20my%20meagre%20savings.%20Despite%20attempting%20to%20seek%20investment%20from%20the%20government%20and%20private%20investors%2C%20I%20struggled%20to%20make%20headway.%20Resorting%20to%20selling%20my%20car%20and%20furniture%2C%20I%20injected%20funds%20into%20the%20project%20and%20borrowed%20money%20from%20friends%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20repay%20them%20upon%20returning%20to%20practice%20if%20things%20did%20not%20work%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20these%20challenges%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deter%20me.%20Fueled%20by%20a%20vision%2C%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20create%20something%20for%20my%20country%2C%20making%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F206730%2Fmedical-app-insurance-cost-cheap-healthcare-c