0been%20living%20without%20basic%20amenities%20like%20power%20and%20road%20connectivity.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20a%20remote%20village%20gets%205G%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Kerala%20and%20a%202012-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20Krishnanunni%20H%20took%20charge%20as%20the%20district%20collector%20of%20Erode%20in%202021.%20It%20was%20during%20his%20regular%20visits%20to%20the%20remote%20parts%20of%20the%20district%20that%20he%20came%20across%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20these%20tribal%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20health%20and%20education%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20usually%20has%20one%20of%20the%20best%20systems%20in%20place.%20For%20example%2C%20Erode%20district%20in%20the%20state%20is%20well%20developed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20remote%20pockets%20like%20Kathirimalai%2C%20which%20are%20located%20deep%20within%20the%20forest%2C%20are%20inaccessible%20given%20its%20geographically%20difficult%20terrain.%20Tribal%20residents%20have%20to%20trek%20for%203-4%20hours%20one%20way%20to%20avail%20health%20services.%20This%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20avail%20of%20any%20other%20welfare%20services%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kathirimalai%20has%20been%20connected%20with%20a%205GHz%20Wi-Fi%20network%20to%20provide%20tele-medicine%20and%20tele-education%20services%20to%20tribal%20residents.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624.jpg%201200